| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2213 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fca021ef-5b26-5bff-8302-f6b0ea89f2ad"
